<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FFAF6A10F7F09C5C141EB1F6" pageId="84" pageNumber="842" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFFAF6A10F7F09C5C145AB17C" blockId="84.[2057,2652,2494,2914]" pageId="84" pageNumber="842">
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFAF6A10F7F09C5C1708B114" authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1916" box="[2060,2312,2565,2598]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Histiotus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="84" pageNumber="842" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="laephotis">Histiotus laephotis</taxonomicName>
has been previously considered a subspecies of 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFAF6A10F6539C681455B17C" authorityName="Poeppig" authorityYear="1835" box="[2479,2645,2609,2638]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Nycticeius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="84" pageNumber="842" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="macrotus">H. macrotus</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFFAF6A10F7F09C0D141EB1F6" blockId="84.[2057,2652,2494,2914]" pageId="84" pageNumber="842">
It is frequently mistaken with 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFAF6A10F63C9C0D145CB147" authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1916" box="[2496,2652,2644,2677]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Histiotus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="84" pageNumber="842" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="laephotis">H. laephotis</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFAF6A10F7B79CD916F7B1AF" baseAuthorityName="Philippi &amp; Landbeck" baseAuthorityYear="1861" box="[2123,2295,2688,2717]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Histiotus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="84" pageNumber="842" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="montanus">H. montanus</taxonomicName>
, therefore, accurate data from literature are scarce. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FFAF6A10F7F79C8A168CB00B" pageId="84" pageNumber="842" type="distribution">
<caption id="90EB6676FFAF6A10F7F79C8A168CB00B" ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6398180" ID-Zenodo-Dep="6398180" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6398180/files/figure.png" inLine="true" pageId="84" pageNumber="842" targetBox="[1444,2035,2497,2910]" targetPageId="84">
