C 
<collectingCountry id="BC83766EFFAF6A10F7049C8A1741B1DE" box="[2296,2369,2771,2796]" name="Chile" pageId="84" pageNumber="842">Chile</collectingCountry>
and NW, C &amp; W 
<collectingCountry id="BC83766EFFAF6A10F7F59CA81699B020" box="[2057,2201,2801,2834]" name="Argentina" pageId="84" pageNumber="842">Argentina</collectingCountry>
. Records from 
<collectingCountry id="BC83766EFFAF6A10F6829CA817BEB020" box="[2430,2494,2801,2834]" name="Peru" pageId="84" pageNumber="842">Peru</collectingCountry>
should be reviewed.
</paragraph>
